Title: Collection of Material about Japanese American Incarceration
Summary: The collection consists primarily of materials from the United States War Relocation Authority related to Japanese Americans and forced removal.
Description.caption: Manzanar High School Yearbook, "Valediction" (page 13), Collection of material about Japanese American incarceration (Collection 131). UCLA Library Special Collections, Charles E. Young Research Library, University of California, Los Angeles.
Description.note: Description of the digitized materials was repurposed from the finding aid for the collection of material about Japanese American Incarceration.
